Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:44.02,Main,Al,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:45.53,Main,Al,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dobre, idem!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:47.96,Main,Mi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Počkaj! Potrebujeme viac informácii!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:52.24,Main,Al,0,0,0,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.72,Main,Mi,0,0,0,,Musí to mať po svojom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.17,Main,Se,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:58.25,Main,Mi,0,0,0,,To je Audium.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:00.97,Main,Se,0,0,0,,Audium?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:02.25,Main,Ay,0,0,0,,Si si istý?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:07.76,Main,S,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hej. Nikdy by som nedokázal zabudnúť na tie hnusné čierne vlny.
